OF:בָּחַר,  choice,  V-Qal-QalPassPrtcpl-ms,  chosen, with_eight, hundred, thousand, man, ~, mighty_men, of_valor, 

T: And Abijah joined the battle with an army of valiant men of war, four hundred thousand chosen men, and Jeroboam set battle against him, with eight hundred thousand chosen men, who were might men of valor. 


2  Chronicles  13-4  וַיָּקָם  אֲבִיָּה  מֵעַל  לְהַר  צְמָרַיִם
OF:קוּם,  stand_up,  Conj-w  |  V-Qal-ConsecImperf-3ms,  he_stood_up, Abijah, on, to_mount, Zemaraim, 

