T: And Abijah sood up on Mount Zemaraim, which is in the mountain of Ephraim, and he said, "Hear me! Jeroboam and all Israel!"


2  Chronicles  13-5  הֲלֹא  לָכֶם  לָדַעַת  כִּי  יְהוָה  אֱלֹהֵי  יִשְׂרָאֵל
