OF:נָתַן,  give,  V-Qal-Perf-3ms,  he_gave, kingdom, to_David, over_Israel, forever, to_him, and_to_his_sons, by_covenant, of_salt. 

T: Should you not to know that Yahweh the God of Israel, he gave the kingdom to David over Israel forever, to him and to his sons, by a covenant of salt. 


2  Chronicles  13-6  וַיָּקָם  יָרָבְעָם  בֶּן־נְבָט  עֶבֶד  שְׁלֹמֹה  בֶן־דָּוִיד
