c  וּרְחַבְעָם  הָיָה  נַעַר  וְרַךְ־לֵבָב
OF:מָיָה,  it_is,  V-Qal-Perf-3ms,  he_was, and_Rehoboam, ~, young, and_inexperienced_of_heart. 

