2  Chronicles  13-12  Behold,  God  is  with  us  at  our  head,  and  his  priests  with  the  trumpets  of  alarm  to  sound  an  alarm  against  you.  Children  of  Israel,  don’t  fight  against  Yahweh,  the  God  of  your  fathers;  for  you  will  not  prosper.”<CM>


